{
  "video_id": "j_GzkjHtFiA",
  "title": "Adventures of an interplanetary architect | Xavier De Kestelier",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12680.0,
      "end_time": 15960.0,
      "text": "I must have been about 12 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15120.0,
      "end_time": 19176.0,
      "text": "when my dad took me to an exhibition on space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19200.0,
      "end_time": 20680.0,
      "text": "not far from here, in Brussels."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21840.0,
      "end_time": 24656.0,
      "text": "And the year was about -- I think it was 1988,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24680.0,
      "end_time": 26520.0,
      "text": "so it was the end of the Cold War."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27280.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "There was a bit of an upmanship going on between the Americans and the Russians"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31400.0,
      "end_time": 33280.0,
      "text": "bringing bits to that exhibition."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 36520.0,
      "text": "NASA brought a big blow-up space shuttle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37800.0,
      "end_time": 42736.0,
      "text": "but the Russians, they brought a Mir space station."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42760.0,
      "end_time": 44815.0,
      "text": "It was actually the training module,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44840.0,
      "end_time": 47336.0,
      "text": "and you could go inside and check it all out."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47360.0,
      "end_time": 48936.0,
      "text": "It was the real thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48960.0,
      "end_time": 51960.0,
      "text": "where the buttons were, where the wires were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51120.0,
      "end_time": 54215.0,
      "text": "where the astronauts were eating, where they were working."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54240.0,
      "end_time": 56136.0,
      "text": "And when I came home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56160.0,
      "end_time": 59440.0,
      "text": "the first thing I did, I started drawing spaceships."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60320.0,
      "end_time": 64376.0,
      "text": "Now, these weren&#39;t science fiction spaceships, no."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64400.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66296.0,
      "text": "They were actually technical drawings."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66320.0,
      "end_time": 68976.0,
      "text": "They were cutaway sections"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69000.0,
      "end_time": 71936.0,
      "text": "of what kind of structure would be made out of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71960.0,
      "end_time": 74520.0,
      "text": "where the wires were, where the screws were."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75600.0,
      "end_time": 78696.0,
      "text": "So fortunately, I didn&#39;t become a space engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78720.0,
      "end_time": 81360.0,
      "text": "but I did become an architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81920.0,
      "end_time": 84696.0,
      "text": "These are some of the projects that I&#39;ve been involved with"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84720.0,
      "end_time": 86976.0,
      "text": "over the last decade and a half."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87000.0,
      "end_time": 90456.0,
      "text": "All these projects are quite different, quite different shapes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90480.0,
      "end_time": 93336.0,
      "text": "and it is because they are built for different environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93360.0,
      "end_time": 94920.0,
      "text": "They have different constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96400.0,
      "end_time": 99456.0,
      "text": "And I think design becomes really interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99480.0,
      "end_time": 103440.0,
      "text": "when you get really harsh constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104160.0,
      "end_time": 107520.0,
      "text": "Now, these projects have been all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108320.0,
      "end_time": 111616.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, this map wasn&#39;t good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111640.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "It was too small."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 115000.0,
      "text": "We had to add this one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115600.0,
      "end_time": 119136.0,
      "text": "because we were going to do a project on the Moon"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 120896.0,
      "text": "for the European Space Agency;"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120920.0,
      "end_time": 123416.0,
      "text": "they asked us to design a Moon habitat --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123440.0,
      "end_time": 126576.0,
      "text": "and one on Mars with NASA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126600.0,
      "end_time": 130919.0,
      "text": "a competition to look at a habitation on Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132280.0,
      "end_time": 135936.0,
      "text": "Whenever you go to another place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135960.0,
      "end_time": 137416.0,
      "text": "as an architect"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137440.0,
      "end_time": 139400.0,
      "text": "and try to design something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140360.0,
      "end_time": 143816.0,
      "text": "you look at the local architecture, the precedents that are there."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143840.0,
      "end_time": 146296.0,
      "text": "Now, on the Moon, it&#39;s kind of difficult, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146320.0,
      "end_time": 147576.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s only this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147600.0,
      "end_time": 150480.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s only the Apollo missions."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151400.0,
      "end_time": 154536.0,
      "text": "So last that we went there, I wasn&#39;t even born yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154560.0,
      "end_time": 157800.0,
      "text": "and we only spent about three days there."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158680.0,
      "end_time": 162936.0,
      "text": "So for me, that&#39;s kind of a long camping trip, isn&#39;t it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162960.0,
      "end_time": 164400.0,
      "text": "but a rather expensive one."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 166480.0,
      "end_time": 168775.0,
      "text": "Now, the tricky thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168800.0,
      "end_time": 172736.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;re going to build on another planet or a moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172760.0,
      "end_time": 176296.0,
      "text": "is how to get it there, how to get it there."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176320.0,
      "end_time": 179335.0,
      "text": "So first of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179360.0,
      "end_time": 182576.0,
      "text": "to get a kilogram, for example, to the Moon&#39;s surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182600.0,
      "end_time": 185200.0,
      "text": "it will cost about 200,000 dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186840.0,
      "end_time": 188216.0,
      "text": "very expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188240.0,
      "end_time": 190480.0,
      "text": "So you want to keep it very light."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 191440.0,
      "end_time": 194416.0,
      "text": "Second, space. Space is limited. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 194440.0,
      "end_time": 196456.0,
      "text": "This is the Ariane 5 rocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196480.0,
      "end_time": 197736.0,
      "text": "The space you have there"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 197760.0,
      "end_time": 202320.0,
      "text": "is about four and a half meters by seven meters, not that much."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 203000.0,
      "end_time": 206136.0,
      "text": "So it needs to be an architectural system"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206160.0,
      "end_time": 210416.0,
      "text": "that is both compact, or compactable, and light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210440.0,
      "end_time": 213790.0,
      "text": "and I think I&#39;ve got one right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214320.0,
      "end_time": 216456.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very compact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 216480.0,
      "end_time": 219550.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s very light."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 220736.0,
      "text": "And actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 220760.0,
      "end_time": 224200.0,
      "text": "this is one I made earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225440.0,
      "end_time": 228936.0,
      "text": "Now, there&#39;s one problem with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 228960.0,
      "end_time": 231440.0,
      "text": "that inflatables"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 232520.0,
      "end_time": 233920.0,
      "text": "are quite fragile."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235360.0,
      "end_time": 236640.0,
      "text": "They need to be protected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 238840.0,
      "end_time": 243200.0,
      "text": "specifically, when you go to a very harsh environment like the Moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245600.0,
      "end_time": 246799.0,
      "text": "Look at it like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 249800.0,
      "end_time": 251336.0,
      "text": "The temperature difference on a Moon base"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251360.0,
      "end_time": 253416.0,
      "text": "could be anything up to 200 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253440.0,
      "end_time": 257336.0,
      "text": "On one side of the base, it could be 100 degrees Celsius"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257360.0,
      "end_time": 259840.0,
      "text": "and on the other side, it could be minus 100 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260399.0,
      "end_time": 262280.0,
      "text": "We need to protect ourselves from that."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263720.0,
      "end_time": 267960.0,
      "text": "The Moon also does not have any magnetic fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269120.0,
      "end_time": 274960.0,
      "text": "which means that any radiation -- solar radiation, cosmic radiation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274120.0,
      "end_time": 275440.0,
      "text": "will hit the surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276320.0,
      "end_time": 278536.0,
      "text": "We need to protect ourselves from that as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 278560.0,
      "end_time": 280160.0,
      "text": "protect the astronauts from that."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 281400.0,
      "end_time": 282616.0,
      "text": "And then third,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 282640.0,
      "end_time": 284416.0,
      "text": "but definitely not last,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 284440.0,
      "end_time": 287800.0,
      "text": "the Moon does not have any atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 288120.0,
      "end_time": 292896.0,
      "text": "which means any meteorites coming into it will not get burned up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 292920.0,
      "end_time": 294296.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ll hit the surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294320.0,
      "end_time": 296599.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why the Moon is full of craters."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297560.0,
      "end_time": 299960.0,
      "text": "Again, we need to protect the astronauts from that."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301160.0,
      "end_time": 302976.0,
      "text": "So what kind of structure do we need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 303000.0,
      "end_time": 307816.0,
      "text": "Well, the best thing is really a cave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 307840.0,
      "end_time": 310256.0,
      "text": "because a cave has a lot of mass, and we need mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 310280.0,
      "end_time": 313256.0,
      "text": "We need mass to protect ourselves from the temperatures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313280.0,
      "end_time": 314895.0,
      "text": "from the radiation"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 314920.0,
      "end_time": 316640.0,
      "text": "and from the meteorites."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 317800.0,
      "end_time": 319440.0,
      "text": "So this is how we solved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320000.0,
      "end_time": 323160.0,
      "text": "We have indeed the blue part, as you can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 323400.0,
      "end_time": 325776.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an inflatable for our Moon base."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325800.0,
      "end_time": 329280.0,
      "text": "It gives a lot of living space and a lot of lab space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 329960.0,
      "end_time": 332775.0,
      "text": "and attached to it you have a cylinder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 332800.0,
      "end_time": 335856.0,
      "text": "and that has all the support structures in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 335880.0,
      "end_time": 339120.0,
      "text": "all the life support and also the airlock."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 340800.0,
      "end_time": 344376.0,
      "text": "And on top of that, we have a structure, that domed structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 344400.0,
      "end_time": 345775.0,
      "text": "that protects ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 345800.0,
      "end_time": 347160.0,
      "text": "has a lot of mass in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 348440.0,
      "end_time": 350576.0,
      "text": "Where are we going to get this material from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 350600.0,
      "end_time": 353696.0,
      "text": "Are we going to bring concrete and cement from Earth to the Moon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 353720.0,
      "end_time": 356256.0,
      "text": "Well, of course not, because it&#39;s way too heavy."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 356280.0,
      "end_time": 357535.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s too expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 357560.0,
      "end_time": 361416.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to go and use local materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 361440.0,
      "end_time": 364536.0,
      "text": "Now, local materials are something we deal with on Earth as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 364560.0,
      "end_time": 366936.0,
      "text": "Wherever we build or whatever country we build in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 366960.0,
      "end_time": 369455.0,
      "text": "we always look at, what are the local materials here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 369480.0,
      "end_time": 372336.0,
      "text": "The problem with the Moon is, what are the local materials?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 372360.0,
      "end_time": 374576.0,
      "text": "Well, there&#39;s not that many."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 374600.0,
      "end_time": 376176.0,
      "text": "Actually, we have one."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 376200.0,
      "end_time": 377400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s moondust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 378480.0,
      "end_time": 383480.0,
      "text": "or, fancier scientific name, regolith, Moon regolith."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 385800.0,
      "end_time": 387376.0,
      "text": "Great thing is, it&#39;s everywhere, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 387400.0,
      "end_time": 389416.0,
      "text": "The surface is covered with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 389440.0,
      "end_time": 392960.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about 20 centimeters up to a few meters everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 394400.0,
      "end_time": 396400.0,
      "text": "But how are we going to build with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396760.0,
      "end_time": 399120.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;re going to use a 3D printer."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 400560.0,
      "end_time": 402776.0,
      "text": "Whenever I ask any of you what a 3D printer is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 406136.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re probably all thinking, well, probably something about this size"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 406160.0,
      "end_time": 410776.0,
      "text": "and it would print things that are about this size."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 410800.0,
      "end_time": 414160.0,
      "text": "So of course I&#39;m not going to bring a massive 3D printer to the Moon"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 414400.0,
      "end_time": 415296.0,
      "text": "to print my Moon base."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 415320.0,
      "end_time": 419320.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to use a much smaller device, something like this one here."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 420640.0,
      "end_time": 423856.0,
      "text": "So this is a small device, a small robot rover,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 423880.0,
      "end_time": 425200.0,
      "text": "that has a little scoop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 426800.0,
      "end_time": 429816.0,
      "text": "and it brings the regolith to the dome"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 429840.0,
      "end_time": 433976.0,
      "text": "and then it lays down a thin layer of regolith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 434000.0,
      "end_time": 437416.0,
      "text": "and then you would have the robot that will solidify it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 437440.0,
      "end_time": 439456.0,
      "text": "layer by layer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 439480.0,
      "end_time": 442416.0,
      "text": "until it creates, after a few months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 442440.0,
      "end_time": 443640.0,
      "text": "the full base."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 445600.0,
      "end_time": 447176.0,
      "text": "You might have noticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 447200.0,
      "end_time": 451416.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s quite a particular structure that we&#39;re printing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 451440.0,
      "end_time": 454200.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve got a little example here."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 455280.0,
      "end_time": 460616.0,
      "text": "What we call this is a closed-cell foam structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 460640.0,
      "end_time": 462816.0,
      "text": "Looks quite natural."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 462840.0,
      "end_time": 464496.0,
      "text": "The reason why we&#39;re using this"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 464520.0,
      "end_time": 466575.0,
      "text": "as part of that shell structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466600.0,
      "end_time": 470360.0,
      "text": "is that we only need to solidify certain parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 471120.0,
      "end_time": 474376.0,
      "text": "which means we have to bring less binder from Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 474400.0,
      "end_time": 476000.0,
      "text": "and it becomes much lighter."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 476840.0,
      "end_time": 478390.0,
      "text": "Now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 479640.0,
      "end_time": 482536.0,
      "text": "that approach of designing something"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 482560.0,
      "end_time": 485496.0,
      "text": "and then covering it with a protective dome"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 485520.0,
      "end_time": 487680.0,
      "text": "we also did for our Mars project."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 488760.0,
      "end_time": 490776.0,
      "text": "You can see it here, three domes."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 490800.0,
      "end_time": 494440.0,
      "text": "And you see the printers printing these dome structures."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 495200.0,
      "end_time": 497616.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a big difference between Mars and the Moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 497640.0,
      "end_time": 499150.0,
      "text": "and let me explain it."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 499400.0,
      "end_time": 502536.0,
      "text": "This diagram shows you to scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 502560.0,
      "end_time": 506256.0,
      "text": "the size of Earth and the Moon and the real distance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 506280.0,
      "end_time": 508200.0,
      "text": "about 400,000 kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 508920.0,
      "end_time": 510400.0,
      "text": "If we then go to Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 511720.0,
      "end_time": 513376.0,
      "text": "the distance from Mars to Earth --"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 513400.0,
      "end_time": 514616.0,
      "text": "and this picture here"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 514640.0,
      "end_time": 519655.0,
      "text": "is taken by the rover on Mars, Curiosity, looking back at Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 519679.0,
      "end_time": 524159.0,
      "text": "You kind of see the little speckle there, that&#39;s Earth, 400 million kilometers away."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 525390.0,
      "end_time": 526496.0,
      "text": "The problem with that distance"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 526520.0,
      "end_time": 530535.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s a thousand times the distance of the Earth to the Moon, pretty far away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 530559.0,
      "end_time": 537550.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s no direct radio contact with, for example, the Curiosity rover."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 537800.0,
      "end_time": 540936.0,
      "text": "So I cannot teleoperate it from Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 540960.0,
      "end_time": 545176.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t say, \"Oh, Mars rover, go left,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 545200.0,
      "end_time": 548320.0,
      "text": "because that signal would take 20 minutes to get to Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 549360.0,
      "end_time": 551976.0,
      "text": "Then the rover might go left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552000.0,
      "end_time": 554976.0,
      "text": "and then it will take another 20 minutes before it can tell me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 555000.0,
      "end_time": 556200.0,
      "text": "\"Oh yeah, I went left.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 556960.0,
      "end_time": 558736.0,
      "text": "So the distance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 558760.0,
      "end_time": 561976.0,
      "text": "so rovers and robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 562000.0,
      "end_time": 564000.0,
      "text": "and going to have to work autonomously."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 565120.0,
      "end_time": 567160.0,
      "text": "The only issue with it"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 567400.0,
      "end_time": 571456.0,
      "text": "is that missions to Mars are highly risky."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 571480.0,
      "end_time": 574936.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve only seen it a few weeks ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 574960.0,
      "end_time": 578416.0,
      "text": "So what if half the mission doesn&#39;t arrive at Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 578440.0,
      "end_time": 579696.0,
      "text": "What do we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 579720.0,
      "end_time": 582816.0,
      "text": "Well, instead of building just one or two rovers"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 582840.0,
      "end_time": 584216.0,
      "text": "like we did on the Moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584240.0,
      "end_time": 586856.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to build hundreds of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 586880.0,
      "end_time": 590415.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a bit like a termite&#39;s mound, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 590440.0,
      "end_time": 593976.0,
      "text": "Termites, I would take half of the colony of the termites away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 594000.0,
      "end_time": 596496.0,
      "text": "they would still be able to build the mound."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 596520.0,
      "end_time": 598536.0,
      "text": "It might take a little bit longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 598560.0,
      "end_time": 599776.0,
      "text": "Same here."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 599800.0,
      "end_time": 602815.0,
      "text": "If half of our rovers or robots don&#39;t arrive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 602840.0,
      "end_time": 606136.0,
      "text": "well, it will take a bit longer, but you will still be able to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 606160.0,
      "end_time": 609216.0,
      "text": "So here we even have three different rovers."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 609240.0,
      "end_time": 611400.0,
      "text": "In the back, you see the digger."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 611520.0,
      "end_time": 614280.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really good at digging regolith."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 614960.0,
      "end_time": 618496.0,
      "text": "Then we have the transporter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 618520.0,
      "end_time": 622336.0,
      "text": "great at taking regolith and bringing it to the structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 622360.0,
      "end_time": 624976.0,
      "text": "And the last ones, the little ones with the little legs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 625000.0,
      "end_time": 626456.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t need to move a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 626480.0,
      "end_time": 629416.0,
      "text": "What they do is they go and sit on a layer of regolith"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 629440.0,
      "end_time": 631376.0,
      "text": "and then microwave it together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 631400.0,
      "end_time": 635120.0,
      "text": "and layer by layer create that dome structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 636160.0,
      "end_time": 637360.0,
      "text": "Now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 639440.0,
      "end_time": 640856.0,
      "text": "we also want to try that out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 640880.0,
      "end_time": 643216.0,
      "text": "so we went out on a road trip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 643240.0,
      "end_time": 648960.0,
      "text": "and we created our own swarm of robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 649640.0,
      "end_time": 650896.0,
      "text": "There you go."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 650920.0,
      "end_time": 653455.0,
      "text": "So we built 10 of those. It&#39;s a small swarm."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 653480.0,
      "end_time": 656496.0,
      "text": "And we took six tons of sand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 656520.0,
      "end_time": 659896.0,
      "text": "and we tried out how these little robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 659920.0,
      "end_time": 662256.0,
      "text": "would actually be able to move sand around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 662280.0,
      "end_time": 664376.0,
      "text": "Earth sand in this case."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 664400.0,
      "end_time": 667656.0,
      "text": "And they were not teleoperated. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 667680.0,
      "end_time": 672550.0,
      "text": "Nobody was telling them go left, go right, or giving them a predescribed path."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 672800.0,
      "end_time": 674296.0,
      "text": "No. They were given a task:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 674320.0,
      "end_time": 677640.0,
      "text": "move sand from this area to that area."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 678280.0,
      "end_time": 681960.0,
      "text": "And if they came across an obstacle, like a rock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 681120.0,
      "end_time": 683496.0,
      "text": "they had to sort it out themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 683520.0,
      "end_time": 685175.0,
      "text": "Or they came across another robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 685200.0,
      "end_time": 688560.0,
      "text": "they had to be able to make decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 688800.0,
      "end_time": 691176.0,
      "text": "Or even if half of them fell out, their batteries died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 691200.0,
      "end_time": 694360.0,
      "text": "they still had to be able to finish that task."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 696120.0,
      "end_time": 699160.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ve talked about redundancy."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 700960.0,
      "end_time": 702816.0,
      "text": "But that was not only with the robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 702840.0,
      "end_time": 704296.0,
      "text": "It was also with the habitats."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 704320.0,
      "end_time": 708120.0,
      "text": "On the Mars project, we decided to do three domes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 710280.0,
      "end_time": 713136.0,
      "text": "because if one didn&#39;t arrive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 713160.0,
      "end_time": 715175.0,
      "text": "the other two could still form a base,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 715200.0,
      "end_time": 717336.0,
      "text": "and that was mainly because each of the domes"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 717360.0,
      "end_time": 721296.0,
      "text": "actually have a life support system built in the floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 721320.0,
      "end_time": 723520.0,
      "text": "so they can work independently."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 724400.0,
      "end_time": 728599.0,
      "text": "So in a way, you might think, well, this is pretty crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 729720.0,
      "end_time": 734216.0,
      "text": "Why would you, as an architect, get involved in space?"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 734240.0,
      "end_time": 737720.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s such a technical field."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 738400.0,
      "end_time": 741456.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;m actually really convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 741480.0,
      "end_time": 746960.0,
      "text": "that from a creative view or a design view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 746120.0,
      "end_time": 752176.0,
      "text": "you are able to solve really hard and really constrained problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 752200.0,
      "end_time": 756160.0,
      "text": "And I really feel that there is a place for design and architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 756400.0,
      "end_time": 759760.0,
      "text": "in projects like interplanetary habitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 760320.0,
      "end_time": 761536.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 761560.0,
      "end_time": 763800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}